---
title: Easy Beef Enchiladas with Baby Gem Salad and Zesty Sour Cream
description: A recipe for enchiladas appeared in Mexico's first ever cookbook, which was published way back in 1831! This is our version of the traditional favourite. Mashing up the beans gives a creamy consistency that we think you'll love. Arriba!
